summary: Some things about my sister after I got her into Bnha
body:
Some things about my sister after I got her into Bnha

  • She went from yelling at me whenever I called bakugo ugly to referring to him as a sweaty bitch
  • She pets Mina whenever she’s on the screen
  • The reason she started watching it was because Momo had big dick energy
  • She ships Kiribaku but isn’t up to date so I keep referring to the moment as ’the moment’ and she yells at me whenever I bring it up
  • She hates Mineta and screams ew whenever he’s on screen
  • She can’t ever remember Todoroki’s name and calls him ’bitch’ every time
  • She ships Momo and Mina even though they’ve never talked
  • Her favorite thing is when Bakugo shouts die and she’s always bringing it into conversations about it
  • She’ll send me cursed messages like ”IIDA JUST ATE MINETA ASS” or ”smh the guys needs to stop being lil bitches and take those towels off” out of nowhere
  • Her favorite is Kirishima and didn’t believe me when I said he wears crocs
  • She always does the Denki thumbs up thing and it bothers me so much
  • The day she learned about Kiribaku she went through the entire tag and read fanfiction all night, and keeps crying ”damnit you made me twelve again”
  • She hates herself bc she got Tumblr just for kiribaku
  • And she’s attached to Tokoyami for no reason

title: Tentando assistir Boku No Hero
body: Faz tempo que eu estou tentando assistir o anime que me recomendam a bastante tempo “Boku No Hero”…Estou na primeira temporada mas enfim vou terminar de assistir. Acho o começo meio clichê e não muito original, mas quem sabe com o tempo o anime melhora com o desenvolvimento dos personagens. Espero que me agrade assim como Bleach e Hunter X Hunter me agradou, mas acho meio difícil pois esses animes tem um lugar muito importante na minha mente.
